Don't forget, JP, you have quite alot of EMP blasts and missiles
raining down at Hell Beast, Rampage, Inferno, and Tankorr.

::Prowl::

Prowl finally reached Cracken, slashing at him with his talons. Deep
in his mind, he knew that the shields of the CF would fall soon, not
that that was a problem. With the Element fully functional and newer
than the Cybertronian Fire, the latter being destroyed wouldn't hurt
them too much. In fact, it might even help. The part of the mind
that's actually him lets the beast take over completely and retreats
to a small corner of his thoughts, planning ahead for uses for the CF.
He knew it would be taken apart anyways, and perhaps this attack could
be used to that purpose.
